children.text: The Hebel wall panels in this area are in contact with the flashings, which will not allow deflection, or moisture and condensation from behind the panels to escape, causing damage to the Hebel system or other building elements.
The Hebel Power Panel external wall design and installation instructions show the following detail for this situation;
This must be properly rectified to prevent failure of the Hebel system, prior to works in this area proceeding any further.
